{
  "texts": [
    "All abstracts from this repository are in English.",
    "Abstracts from NBER and AEA were compared to those from RePEc to remove duplicates from the dataset.",
    "The combined dataset finished with 2.8 million English abstracts.",
    "Oil Markets (OM)The OM dataset is used to fine-tune the sentiment analysis of the different models.",
    "All source information comes from news articles in \"The Oil Bulletin.\""
  ]
}